about.description: Provides the conda env interface to Conda environments.
about.summary: Tools for interacting with conda environments.

name: conda-env
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = "2.6.0" %}

package:
  name: conda-env
  version: {{ version }}

build:
  number: 1
  noarch: python

test:
  requires:
    - python
  commands:
    - conda env create --help

about:
  home: https://github.com/conda/conda-env
  summary: Tools for interacting with conda environments.
  license: BSD 3-Clause
  
  description: |
    Provides the conda env interface to Conda environments.
  doc_url: https://conda.io/docs/user-guide/overview.html
  dev_url: https://github.com/conda/conda-env
  doc_source_url: https://github.com/conda/conda-docs

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jakirkham
    - kalefranz
    - mcg1969
    - msarahan
    - pelson
